OL,3,CHusband said he would 'cut up and
OL,4,Cdissolve wife's body', court hears
OL,6,FThe mother of a woman who took her own
OL,7,Flife after she was allegedly abused by
OL,8,Fher husband has told a court that he
OL,9,Ftold her daughter he would "snap her
OL,10,Fneck, cut up her body and dissolve it
OL,11,Fin acid".
OL,13,FChristopher Trybus, from Swindon, is
OL,14,Faccused of the manslaughter of Tarryn
OL,15,FBaird, who died from hanging in
OL,16,FNovember 2017 at the age of 34. Trybus
OL,17,Falso faces charges of controlling and
OL,18,Fcoercive behaviour and two charges of
OL,19,Frape, alleged to have happened in
OL,20,FOctober and November 2016.
OL,26,@qD@\OUsD@HO]
