OL,3,CHusband said he would 'cut up and
OL,4,Cdissolve wife's body', court hears
OL,6,FThe coercive control charge alleges
OL,7,Fthat 43-year-old Trybus controlled Ms
OL,8,FBaird through using and threatening
OL,9,Fviolence towards her, sexually
OL,10,Fassaulting her, monitoring her
OL,11,Fwhereabouts, limiting access to
OL,12,Ffinance, threatening to reveal private
OL,13,Finformation to her family and
OL,14,Fisolating her from her family.
OL,16,FTarryn's mother Michelle Baird told
OL,17,Fjurors she had seen bruises on her
OL,18,Fdaughter's body and described how she
OL,19,Fhad become withdrawn from her family.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
