OL,3,CHusband said he would 'cut up and
OL,4,Cdissolve wife's body', court hears
OL,6,FThe court heard Ms Baird and Trybus
OL,7,Fcame to the UK from their home country
OL,8,Fof South Africa in 2007 and were
OL,9,Fmarried two years later. Mrs Baird
OL,10,Fdescribed how she, her husband and
OL,11,Ftheir son joined her daughter in
OL,12,FEngland and moved into a property
OL,13,Fcloser to her home in 2014. Mrs Baird
OL,14,Fsaid that a "couple of weeks" before
OL,15,Fher daughter's death, Ms Baird told
OL,16,Fher the defendant had threatened to
OL,17,Fkill her and dispose of her body.
OL,26,@vD@MOUvD@]O]
