OL,3,CHusband said he would 'cut up and
OL,4,Cdissolve wife's body', court hears
OL,6,FMrs Baird said: "Tarryn said
OL,7,FChristopher said he would 'snap my
OL,8,Fneck in a heartbeat, cut up my body,
OL,9,Fdissolve it in acid and nobody would
OL,10,Ffind me'.
OL,12,F"I said to Christopher 'Are you sick?
OL,13,FIf I don't find my daughter I will
OL,14,Fcome looking for her'.
OL,16,F"He laughed and began to tell me how
OL,17,Fhe would do it. He wasn't saying it in
OL,18,Fa jokey way at all."
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@AOUxD@AOUzD@TO]
