OL,3,CHusband said he would 'cut up and
OL,4,Cdissolve wife's body', court hears
OL,6,FMrs Baird sobbed as she told that the
OL,7,Fcourt that as she was leaving, she
OL,8,Fdiscussed with her daughter
OL,9,Farrangements for Christmas and she
OL,10,Fsaid her daughter said to her: "There
OL,11,Fwon't be a Christmas this year."
OL,13,FMrs Baird also told the court that
OL,14,Fafter an apparent attempt by her
OL,15,Fdaughter to take her own life in
OL,16,FSeptember 2017, they had a family
OL,17,Fmeeting because she was "very
OL,18,Fconcerned" for her.
OL,26,@rD@`OUsD@`O]yD@YOUzD@JO]
