OL,3,CHusband said he would 'cut up and
OL,4,Cdissolve wife's body', court hears
OL,6,FShe said: "I did put forward that
OL,7,FTarryn needed 24-hour care and they
OL,8,Fshould look at private care as they
OL,9,Fcould afford it."
OL,11,FMrs Baird said that this did not
OL,12,Fhappen and added: "She told me
OL,13,FChristopher thought it was too
OL,14,Fexpensive, #6,000 a week, and he
OL,15,Fthought it wasn't the right fit for
OL,16,Fher."
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@SOUxD@EO]
