OL,3,CHusband said he would 'cut up and
OL,4,Cdissolve wife's body', court hears
OL,6,FMrs Baird also described how her
OL,7,Fdaughter became "extremely concerned"
OL,8,Fwhen a police officer "wanted to
OL,9,Farrest" Trybus in September 2017 after
OL,10,Fher daughter's counsellor had reported
OL,11,Fthat she had been domestically abused.
OL,13,FMrs Baird said: "She was concerned
OL,14,Fabout it because he had to have a
OL,15,Fclear record for the work he did."
OL,26,@oD@QOUoD@eO]pD@WOUqD@GO]uD@QOUwD@bO]
